##Inicializacija metod 

##################################################
## Buy stocks if you have money simulation [WITH PROVISION]
###################################################
#pridobi celoten denar, ki ti pripada 
def getAllMoneyFromStoks(tmp_kapital,info_list,money,bought_stocks,bought_dividents,tmp_day):
    #prodaj vse delnice
    #Get money from stocks
    counter  = 0
    for x in range(len(bought_stocks[0])):
        if(bought_stocks[0][counter] < tmp_day):
            tmp_money = money
            money_from_sell  = bought_stocks[2][counter]*(bought_stocks[1][counter])
            profit = money_from_sell - bought_stocks[4][counter]
              #---------OBDAVČITEV DOBIČKA 30% ---------------
            if(profit > 0):
                profit = profit * 0.7
            tmp_kapital = tmp_kapital + profit    
            money =money + bought_stocks[4][counter] + profit #cena * število
            
            ind = len(info_list[0])
            info_list[0].append(ind) #zap_id
            info_list[1].append("SELL")    #akcija
            info_list[2].append(tmp_money)    #zacetni kapital
            info_list[3].append(bought_stocks[3][counter])    #simbol
            info_list[4].append(bought_stocks[0][counter])    #buy on / sell on [date]
            info_list[5].append(bought_stocks[1][counter])    #cena
            info_list[6].append(bought_stocks[2][counter])    #kolicina
            info_list[7].append(money)    #koncni kapital
            
            del bought_stocks[0][counter]
            del bought_stocks[1][counter]
            del bought_stocks[2][counter]
            del bought_stocks[3][counter]
            del bought_stocks[4][counter]
        else: 
            counter = counter + 1 
    #prodaj vse dividende
    counter  = 0
    for x in range(len(bought_dividents[0])):
        if(bought_dividents[0][counter] < tmp_day):
            tmp_money = money
            #---------OBDAVČITEV DIVIDENDE 30% ---------------
            money =money + bought_dividents[1][counter]*bought_dividents[2][counter]*0.7
            tmp_kapital = tmp_kapital + bought_dividents[1][counter]*bought_dividents[2][counter]*0.7
            ind = len(info_list[0])
            info_list[0].append(ind) #zap_id
            info_list[1].append("GET")    #akcija
            info_list[2].append(tmp_money)    #zacetni kapital
            info_list[3].append(bought_dividents[3][counter])    #simbol
            info_list[4].append(bought_dividents[0][counter])    #buy on / sell on [date]
            info_list[5].append(bought_dividents[1][counter])    #cena
            info_list[6].append(bought_dividents[2][counter])    #kolicina
            info_list[7].append(money)  

            del bought_dividents[0][counter]
            del bought_dividents[1][counter]
            del bought_dividents[2][counter]
            del bought_dividents[3][counter]
        else: 
            #print(bought_dividents[0][counter], "<",tmp_day )
            counter = counter + 1
    return tmp_kapital,info_list,money,bought_stocks,bought_dividents
  
#---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------    
##### Kupi delnico
#---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------    
def buyStocks(info_list,rek_data,money,index_path,tmp_index,bought_stocks,bought_dividents):
    #Dodaj indek na index_path
    index_path.append(tmp_index)
    
    #odstej denar
    tmp_money = money
    num_of_bought_stocks = int(money/rek_data[3][tmp_index])
    money = money - (num_of_bought_stocks *rek_data[3][tmp_index])
    
    #zapiši v info list
    ind = len(info_list[0])
    info_list[0].append(ind) #zap_id
    info_list[1].append("BUY")    #akcija
    info_list[2].append(tmp_money)    #zacetni kapital
    info_list[3].append(rek_data[6][tmp_index])    #simbol
    info_list[4].append(rek_data[0][tmp_index])    #buy on / sell on [date]
    info_list[5].append(rek_data[3][tmp_index])    #cena
    info_list[6].append(num_of_bought_stocks)    #kolicina
    info_list[7].append(money)    #koncni kapital
    
    #print("BUY: Zac_kap:",tmp_money,"|sym:",rek_data[6][tmp_index],"|buy on:",rek_data[0][tmp_index],"|price:",rek_data[3][tmp_index],"|Num:",num_of_bought_stocks,"|money:",money) 
    
    #DOdaj delnico na bought_stocks
    bought_stocks[0].append(rek_data[1][tmp_index]) #ex_date
    bought_stocks[1].append(rek_data[4][tmp_index]) #price_on_ex_day_open
    bought_stocks[2].append(num_of_bought_stocks) #number_of_dividents_bought
    bought_stocks[3].append(rek_data[6][tmp_index]) #simbol
    bought_stocks[4].append(tmp_money-money) #------------------> Cena nakupa
    
    #DOdaj dividendo na bought_dividents
    bought_dividents[0].append(rek_data[2][tmp_index]) #pay_d
    bought_dividents[1].append(rek_data[5][tmp_index]) #dividents_price
    bought_dividents[2].append(num_of_bought_stocks)   #number_of_dividents_bought
    bought_dividents[3].append(rek_data[6][tmp_index]) #simbol
    
    
    return info_list,rek_data,money,index_path,tmp_index,bought_stocks,bought_dividents

#---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------    
#Pridobi denar od prodaje delnic  
#---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------    
def getMoneyFromStoks(tmp_kapital,info_list,tmp_day,money,bought_stocks,bought_dividents):
    #Get money from stocks
    counter = 0;
    for x in range(len(bought_stocks[0])):
        if(bought_stocks[0][counter] < tmp_day):
            tmp_money = money
            money_from_sell  = bought_stocks[2][counter]*(bought_stocks[1][counter])
            profit = money_from_sell - bought_stocks[4][counter]
            #---------OBDAVČITEV DOBIČKA 30% ---------------
            if(profit > 0):
                profit = profit * 0.7
            tmp_kapital = tmp_kapital + profit
           # print( bought_stocks[4][counter], profit)
            money =money + bought_stocks[4][counter] + profit #cena * število
            #zapiši v info list
            ind = len(info_list[0])
            info_list[0].append(ind) #zap_id
            info_list[1].append("SELL")    #akcija
            info_list[2].append(tmp_money)    #zacetni kapital
            info_list[3].append(bought_stocks[3][counter])    #simbol
            info_list[4].append(bought_stocks[0][counter])    #buy on / sell on [date]
            info_list[5].append(bought_stocks[1][counter])    #cena
            info_list[6].append(bought_stocks[2][counter])    #kolicina
            info_list[7].append(money)    #koncni kapital
            
            #print("SELL Zac_kap: ",tmp_money,"|sym:",bought_stocks[3][counter],"|sell date:",bought_stocks[0][counter],"|amount:",bought_stocks[2][counter],"|Money:",money)
            #izbrisi iz seznama
            del bought_stocks[0][counter]
            del bought_stocks[1][counter]
            del bought_stocks[2][counter]
            del bought_stocks[3][counter]
            del bought_stocks[4][counter]
        else:
            counter = counter + 1
    
    #Get money from divident
    counter = 0;
    for x in range(len(bought_dividents[0])):
        if(bought_dividents[0][counter] < tmp_day):
            tmp_money = money
             #---------OBDAVČITEV DIVIDENDE 30% ---------------
            money =money + bought_dividents[2][counter]*(bought_dividents[1][counter]) * 0.7 #cena * število
            tmp_kapital = tmp_kapital + bought_dividents[2][counter]*(bought_dividents[1][counter]) * 0.7 
            #zapiši v info list
            ind = len(info_list[0])
            info_list[0].append(ind) #zap_id
            info_list[1].append("GET")    #akcija
            info_list[2].append(tmp_money)    #zacetni kapital
            info_list[3].append(bought_dividents[3][counter])    #simbol
            info_list[4].append(bought_dividents[0][counter])    #buy on / sell on [date]
            info_list[5].append(bought_dividents[1][counter])    #cena
            info_list[6].append(bought_dividents[2][counter])    #kolicina
            info_list[7].append(money)    #koncni kapital
            #print("GET  Zac_kap: ",tmp_money,"sym:",bought_dividents[3][counter],"sell date: ",bought_dividents[0][counter],"amount:",bought_dividents[2][counter], "Money:",money)
           
            #izbrisi iz seznama
            del bought_dividents[0][counter]
            del bought_dividents[1][counter]
            del bought_dividents[2][counter]
            del bought_dividents[3][counter]
        else:
            counter = counter + 1              
    return tmp_kapital,info_list,tmp_day,money,bought_stocks,bought_dividents
